{"tid":921058,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【賊喊捉賊】浙江大媽燒酒被偷制服賊人報警　協助警方調查卻被揭偷車","createTime":"2018-11-29T09:25:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T09:48:00.000Z","uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"db7d094b1a4523d7d48fa27e36df66e0e67719ba","tid":921058,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:25:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181129/s00004/b2402672cac1dac4582bf8eb9f79cdb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181129%2Fs00004%2Fb2402672cac1dac4582bf8eb9f79cdb1.jpg&h=95789bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n浙江紹興嵊州市一名中年婦被一名男子偷去她車庫內的燒酒，報案後隨警員回警署協助調查，卻被警方發現她涉及另一宗盜竊案，她承認今年9月中旬曾盜竊一輛三輪車，正接受警方進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n嵊州市三江警署在上周四（22日）接報，經調查後指一名無業男子，在當天潛入未有關緊捲簾門的車庫，隨後偷了部分燒酒，但被商姓的中年女事主發現，兩人在現場扭打，身材瘦小的男子反抗，並傷及女事主手指。<br />\n<br />\n商姓女子制服男子後報警求助，並主動到警署協助調查，但有警員留意到她，隨即翻查另一宗案件的現場閉路電視，結果發現她樣貌與疑犯相似。在警員追問下，她承認曾在9月中旬盜竊一輛三輪車。<br />\n<br />\n被指偷取燒酒的男子因涉嫌搶劫罪被捕，而商姓女子則涉嫌盜竊單車，而正接受進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n（中新網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181129/s00004/1543480805619\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181129%2Fs00004%2F1543480805619&d=oW2ZKT0grFf0NVj5EkmC2DM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=9b8ba6ab\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181129%2Fs00004%2F1543480805619&h=98a02fc3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181129/s00004/1543480805619</a><br />\n<br />\n不用分那麼細 中國人都是賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c59f068e37428c2f953d114a02d5beb22790486","tid":921058,"uid":150609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T09:46:19.000Z","msg":"厲害了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f570964608098b7ddb70b655dbfef6e460